					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Using Online Reviews to Win New Customers" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20150726000431-shutterstock-85447915.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
